WEBVTT

00:01.114 --> 00:03.537
Man is a determined creature,...

00:06.125 --> 00:13.182
...no matter the circumstance, opposition, or even understanding.

00:14.920 --> 00:26.364
There's an inherent calling to seek, push, improve, transcend.

00:28.653 --> 00:30.315
It's a perpetual process,...

00:32.742 --> 00:39.733
...a necessity for human spirit that inspired our own evolution.

00:41.409 --> 00:45.862
Because if your quest is to build the world's smartest luxury SUV for mankind,...

00:46.737 --> 00:49.942
...you must hold yourself to the standard of mankind.

